    <p class="fade-in text-xs md:text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-semibold text-muted-text mb-12 md:mb-16 text-center">
      The problem isn't passion. It's infrastructure.
    </p>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 md:gap-16 mb-12 md:mb-16">
      <div class="fade-in text-center">
        <span class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-orange counter" data-target="65">0</span><span class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-orange">%</span>
        <p class="text-base font-semibold text-dark mt-3 mb-1">of Australian charities are small</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-text leading-relaxed">Most get almost no operational support.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="fade-in text-center" style="transition-delay: 0.1s;">
        <span class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-orange counter" data-target="50">0</span><span class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-orange">%</span>
        <p class="text-base font-semibold text-dark mt-3 mb-1">run entirely by volunteers</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-text leading-relaxed">No budget for operational staff.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="fade-in text-center" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
        <span class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-orange counter" data-target="40">0</span><span class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-orange">%</span>
        <p class="text-base font-semibold text-dark mt-3 mb-1">can't implement digital tools</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-text leading-relaxed">Priced out by enterprise software.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="fade-in text-center text-base md:text-lg text-muted-text max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      The sector is full of people giving everything. They deserve support that matches that commitment.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

